Pre-Game Insights: Spain has topped Group B with a perfect record of nine points and is the only team to reach the round of 16 without conceding a goal.
La Roja came from behind to secure a 4-1 victory over Georgia in the round of 16.
Spain's trio of Lamine Yamal, Alvaro Morata, and Nico Williams has been crucial in breaking the German defense.
Germany has been exceptional in front of goal, having scored a total of ten goals in the tournament so far.
Players like Jamal Musiala, Kai Havertz, and Florian Wirtz are in contention for the Golden Boot.
Die Mannschaft finished at the top of Group A with seven points and defeated Denmark 2-0 in the round of 16.
